file_content.text: Don't use this line again. It could alert them.
Now, we've got no specs on this place, nothing. But anyone in the cells, assume they're one of ours and spring them.
Your main target is Ako Domi. He's a Jedi, led the rescue effort on Sullust that kept the Empire from enslaving half the planet, but got caught himself.
I'll save him. You don't need to convince me.
I'm on my way.
I think with all of you in there, you've got a chance.
The Republic's lucky to have you.
The Republic should count itself lucky to have someone like you.
Am I on my own in here?
Are you sending backup?
I'll do what I can, but we're past the window. We can't get anyone else in until you shut the whole place down.
I'll kill whoever's got him.
That seems like the right sort of attitude for a place like this.
I'll send a team to wait outside the shields. They can back you up if you need it on the way out.
Good luck.
Hang on, our slicers are trying to tap the line....
Got it! That's fantastic! I can't believe you made it into Camp 27. On your own, I mean. We've gotten plenty of guys in the other way.
Don't let it go to your head, though. There's no telling what the Empire's hiding in here.
Do we have cell numbers or something? Let's get in and out, fast.
Where to next?
When I'm done, there won't be anything but bones.
I will destroy this place.
Ha. From your lips to the Emperor's ears, my friend.
I'm not afraid.
Yeah? Talk to me again when you're done.
